### Week 2 Day 9

// Normal

- Create new app “CustomSlider”
- Create new file “SimpleSlider” based on type “UIView”
- IBDesignable & IBInspectable (the slider should be viewable in storyboard)
- slider needs to be created by CoreGraphics
- touches moved will update slider button position and current value
- current value needs to be IBInspectable
- color of slider should be controlled by IBInspectable